cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.SI 

The paper deals with cross-modality visual search, which involves computer vision and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques such as matrix factorization and binary code learning, which are relevant to categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also deals with information retrieval, which is relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
